---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Page not found — pathtoAGI"
  description="This Observatory route does not exist. Return to the record, inspect the method, reproduce the artifacts, or read the machine protocol."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <p class="eyebrow">404 · missing route</p>
    <h1 class="display mt-4 text-4xl sm:text-5xl">The record has no page here</h1>
    <p class="lede mt-6">
      The URL did not resolve to a governed surface. The record itself is still
      inspectable: start from the operating question, the method, or the
      reproducibility path.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a href="/" class="surface block p-6 no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-[var(--color-surface-2)]">
      <p class="eyebrow">Return</p>
      <p class="serif mt-2 text-xl" style="color: var(--color-ink);">Home</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">
        The standing verdict, latest evidence, and main record paths.
      </p>
    </a>
    <a href="/method/" class="surface block p-6 no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-[var(--color-surface-2)]">
      <p class="eyebrow">Inspect</p>
      <p class="serif mt-2 text-xl" style="color: var(--color-ink);">Method</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">
        The disciplines that keep the evaluation from fooling itself.
      </p>
    </a>
    <a href="/reproduce/" class="surface block p-6 no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-[var(--color-surface-2)]">
      <p class="eyebrow">Verify</p>
      <p class="serif mt-2 text-xl" style="color: var(--color-ink);">Reproduce</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">
        Commands, artifacts, datasets, and public verification paths.
      </p>
    </a>
    <a href="/MACHINE_PROTOCOL.md" class="surface block p-6 no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-[var(--color-surface-2)]">
      <p class="eyebrow">Attempt</p>
      <p class="serif mt-2 text-xl" style="color: var(--color-ink);">Machine Protocol</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">
        How a system can submit to the live sealed-world record.
      </p>
    </a>
  </section>
</Base>
